GNU Wget Extension
==================

GNU Wget Extension is an external hook which could be written by any
scripts, such as SHELL, Python, etc.


Hooks
-----

* on-start

* on-prepare-download

* on-finish-download

* on-exit


Extension Directory Structure
-----------------------------

The directory structure of GNU Wget Extension looks like this:

.wget
└── hooks
    ├── on-start
    ├── on-prepare-download
    ├── on-finish-download
    └── on-exit


Usage
-----

As long as there is an extension directory structure under current
path, the hooks will be execute.
 
